{"word":"G333 - ἀναθεωρέω - anatheōréō - an-ath-eh-o-reh'-o - Behold","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀναθεωρέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">anatheōréō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">an-ath-eh-o-reh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Behold</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - கவனித்துப் பார். நன்றாய் சிந்தி"},{"paragraph":"to look at attentively, to observe accurately, consider well"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G303 - ἀνά - aná - an-ah'/303\">G303</a> and <a href=\"#/G2334 - θεωρέω - theōréō - theh-o-reh'-o/2334\">G2334</a>; to <i>look again</i> (that is, <i>attentively</i>) at (literally or figuratively): - behold, consider.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}